Intro: Follow a teenage girl and a trio of fallen gods on a perilous journey as they attempt to bring an end to a demonic reign of chaos and restore balance to their world. Inspired by the 16th Century Chinese fable “Journey to the West.”

Episodes.Intro: A girl uncovers a statue of the legendary Monkey King, but in order to release this ancient God from his stone prison she must first find his golden crown, a crown that has fallen into the hands of Demons.
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x1

Episodes.Intro: While Monkey and Pigsy smuggle themselves into Davari’s banquet, Tripitaka must work out the means of controlling the secret army of the Font Demons before Davari can reveal the extent of his new powers.
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x10

Episodes.Intro: Having released the Monkey King, Tripitaka is shocked to find him indifferent to the Scholar’s mission. Struggling to keep him on side, and still being pursued by Demons, she finds help in the unlikeliest of places.
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x2

Episodes.Intro: When Monkey and Sandy find themselves prisoners to Princess Locke, an escaped Tripitaka must convince Pigsy to abandon his mistress and help her rescue the two Gods.
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x3

Episodes.Intro: As the heroes set off to the Western Mountains they are intercepted by a gang of rebel bandits, who worship the legend of the Monkey King. When the leader discovers Tripitaka can control the crown he plans to capture Monkey.
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x4

Episodes.Intro: Monkey, Pigsy and Sandy are glamoured by a mystical shamanic Demon and taken to a strange prison called the Breaking Ground.
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x5

Episodes.Intro: As Monkey travels further into his past Tripitaka must act quickly before he is lost forever. Using the sutra, she is able to find a way to go after Monkey, and in doing so unravels the mystery of his imprisonment.
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x6

Episodes.Intro: As Tripitaka, Monkey, Pigsy and Sandy flee from the Shaman and his Demonic henchman, they seek shelter in a sprawling forest.
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x7

Episodes.Intro: Tripitaka leaves the quest to go in search of her mother, but Sandy won’t let her travel alone, and the two journey to the North Water.
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x8

Episodes.Intro: As Monkey and Pigsy hide in plain sight within the walls of Davari’s palace, Tripitaka realises why Davari is so determined to translate the Sacred Scrolls. Can she stop him completing the translation before it’s too late?
Episodes.Name: The New Legends of Monkey 1x9

Name: The New Legends of Monkey

Links.Name: The One with the Baby Carrot

Intro: Bored and unhappy as the Lord of Hell, Lucifer Morningstar abandoned his throne and retired to Los Angeles, where he has teamed up with LAPD detective Chloe Decker to take down criminals. But the longer he’s away from the underworld, the greater the threat that the worst of humanity could escape.

Episodes.Intro: Upon leaving hell, Lucifer Morningstar retreats to Los Angeles for a more exciting life. When the murder of a friend connects him with LAPD detective Chloe Decker, Lucifer becomes intrigued with the idea of punishing criminals, sending the devil himself into a struggle between good and evil.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x1

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer and Chloe are tasked with solving the murder of a prominent restaurateur. When they meet his son, they suspect he played a part in the death. Meanwhile, Chloe’s mom returns home, sending Chloe’s life into upheaval, as Lucifer learns his own dysfunctional family isn’t nearly as unique as he thought.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x10

Episodes.Intro: When philanthropist Tim Dunlear is found dead, Lucifer explores his good side by becoming a benefactor for Tim’s glitzy Los Angeles charity.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x11

Episodes.Intro: When a woman is found dead on the Hollywood Walk of Fame – with her body twisted into the shape of a pentagram – the investigation leads Lucifer and team into the world of Satanists, where they soon realize, evil doesn’t always live where we expect it to.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x12

Episodes.Intro: When Lucifer is framed for murder, he and Chloe must work together to clear his name and prove the identity of the true killer.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x13

Episodes.Intro: When a movie star’s son is killed after being chased by the paparazzi, Chloe takes a deep look into the case with a little help from Lucifer. Meanwhile, Maze and Amenadiel continue to encourage Lucifer to go back to hell.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x2

Episodes.Intro: When a 22-year-old future superstar quarterback wakes up to find a dead girl floating in his swimming pool, he turns to his friend, Lucifer, for help. Lucifer enlists Chloe to investigate the case, which leads to the world of big money sports and people who will literally kill to be number one.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x3

Episodes.Intro: In an effort to get over his infatuation with Chloe, Lucifer decides that he must seduce her. Meanwhile the two team up on a missing girl case and Amenadiel confronts Maze about his concerns about Lucifer.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x4

Episodes.Intro: After a shooting occurs at a fashion show and a young woman is killed, Lucifer becomes intrigued by the danger of the situation and begs Chloe to get in on the case. Meanwhile, when Maze admits to Amenadiel that she wants to go back to hell, he sets his sights on Dr. Linda.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x5

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer bails on Chloe when he becomes bored with her investigation into a ruthless biker gang murder. However, when he discovers something was stolen during the crime that was very personal to him, he demands that Chloe let him rejoin the case.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x6

Episodes.Intro: In attempt to find the contents of his stolen container, Lucifer enlists the help of an unlikely ally. Meanwhile, Chloe digs deeper into the Palmetto case, uncovering a lead that might finally expose the truth.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x7

Episodes.Intro: When a therapist is murdered, Lucifer and Chloe enlist the help of Dr. Linda to look into possible suspects. Meanwhile, Malcolm confronts Chloe about the night he was shot, and Lucifer experiences his first bout of jealousy.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x8

Episodes.Intro: A priest seeks out Lucifer’s help when he suspects an underground drug operation has set up shop at a neighborhood youth center. Meanwhile, Malcolm manipulates a way to keep an eye on Dan.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 1x9

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer is distracted by his mother’s escape from hell, as he and Chloe investigate the murder of a stand-in actress. Meanwhile, Chloe’s faith in Lucifer is tested by the new medical examiner, Ella. Also, Amenadiel hopes to rein in Lucifer’s wild side, as they both deal with the absence of Maze.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x1

Episodes.Intro: Charlotte is determined to get Lucifer to leave Earth by turning Chloe against him. Meanwhile, Amenadiel has begun working as Charlotte’s soldier, which makes Maze question his loyalty.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x10

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer and Chloe investigate the murder of two victims, who happen to be Lucifer’s ex-flames.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x11

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer and Chloe investigate a mysterious masked killer who is poisoning college students.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x12

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer must find the antidote to the Professor’s poison before it kills Chloe. He travels to hell to find the Professor’s soul and get him to turn over the antidote. While he’s there, he is forced to confront his guilt about Uriel’s death. Mom heads to hell to get Lucifer back, but Lucifer still feels betrayed by his parents because of something he discovers.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x13

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer returns to the city with a new bride in tow, oblivious to the distress his absence has caused. Determined to restore his working relationship with Chloe, he inserts himself into the investigation of the murder of an up-and-coming band’s lead singer.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x14

Episodes.Intro: When it is discovered that the flaming sword is the only hope for the family returning home safely, the pressure is on for Lucifer to control what he has never been able to control before – his emotions – in order to ignite it. Meanwhile, Chloe wants to air some emotions of her own, but when a therapist and head of admissions at a prestigious private school turns up dead, the team must get to the bottom of it.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x15

Episodes.Intro: When a grisly murder takes place at an insane asylum, the prime suspect calls himself God. After realizing that this man could actually be his father, Lucifer struggles with his feelings towards him and tries to find the truth, all while trying to discover who the real killer is.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x16

Episodes.Intro: When the man who had the final piece of the Flaming Sword is murdered and the piece goes missing, Mom joins Chloe and Lucifer on the case to track down the killer. But when Lucifer gets sidelined, Maze recruits him to help save Dr. Linda’s endangered career and confronts him about the secrets he’s been keeping.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x17

Episodes.Intro: After Charlotte accidentally charbroils a man to death in self-defense, Lucifer must try and keep Chloe from figuring out the truth. Lucifer puts Maze in charge of finding Charlotte and Amenadiel, who have both gone missing in light of recent circumstances, while he finds a permanent solution for the ticking-time-bomb he calls Mom.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x18

Episodes.Intro: When Lucifer’s mother, Charlotte, turns up at the scene of a grizzly murder pleading innocence, Lucifer is hesitant to believe her tale. Not wanting to leave her on her own, he instructs Maze to babysit her – and not to torture her, allowing him to investigate the case with Chloe.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x2

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer and Chloe investigate a gruesome murder after a video of the crime surfaces on social media. When a second video appears, they realize they have a serial killer on their hands. Meanwhile, Lucifer’s mom returns as Charlotte Richards. Also, Amenadiel, struggling with his loss of power, has an appointment with Linda.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x3

Episodes.Intro: After the bodies of two young L.A. transplants are found poisoned, Chloe and Lucifer hunt for the killer. Upon Maze convincing Chloe to go out for drinks, which the detective perceives as an act of friendship, but is actually part of a bet between Maze and Lucifer, the two make a shocking decision.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x4

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer is excited to investigate the murder of his favorite action movie hero, Wesley Cabot. Longtime rival Rolf Van Zandt initially is a suspect, but the investigation soon shifts. Meanwhile, Uriel shows up and Amenadiel is forced to come clean about his lost powers. Also, Lucifer and Uriel fight about Chloe and their mother.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x5

Episodes.Intro: Guilty and self-destructive, Lucifer clashes with Chloe during an investigation, leading her to team up with Dan instead. Meanwhile, Amenadiel bonds with Charlotte, and Maze takes Trixie trick-or-treating.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x6

Episodes.Intro: When the prisoner convicted of killing Chloe’s father is murdered, new evidence suggests he was actually framed. Meanwhile, Maze tries to find a job and Lucifer shadows Dan in order to learn how to be “normal”.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x7

Episodes.Intro: Following the murder of the owner of the building in which Lux is located, Lucifer and Chloe search for the killer, while Lucifer also deals with the fact that the new owner wants to evict him and demolish the place. Lucifer goes to great lengths to protect his home, and is entirely shocked when Chloe is supportive of him. Meanwhile, Maze and Amenadiel follow Charlotte around, as she comes up with a plan to upset Lucifer enough to want to leave earth and go back to Heaven.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 2x9

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer enlists Chloe’s help to determine why he woke up in the desert with his wings on his back again, which could be related to an active crime scene.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x1

Episodes.Intro: With the Sinnerman in custody, Lucifer is prepared to go to any length to get his devil face back. Meanwhile, Trixie is introduced to Charlotte and questions the relationship she has with her father. The Season 3 fall finale.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x10

Episodes.Intro: In a flashback episode that takes place when Lucifer first came to LA, Amenadiel comes to retrieve his fallen brother, but is shocked when he is mugged. Amenadiel enlists Lucifer’s help to track down the mugger and Lucifer, in turn, offers his assistance – but only in exchange for a favor. Meanwhile, Chloe and Dan – who are still married – investigate the murder of an MMA fighter, Aidan Scott, at the hands of the same killer who mugged Amenadiel.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x11

Episodes.Intro: After Lt. Pierce’s true identity is revealed, Lucifer tries to figure out his motives. In order to earn Chloe’s assistance in his investigation of Pierce, Lucifer goes above and beyond to help her solve the murder of a professional surfer. Meanwhile, Amenadiel deals with a personal health issue.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x12

Episodes.Intro: When an ecstasy cook-turned-chemistry-teacher is found murdered in a cozy Los Angeles suburb, Lucifer and Pierce must go undercover to help track down the killer. Meanwhile, Maze has a newfound attraction for someone that she used to despise and Charlotte has a revelation.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x13

Episodes.Intro: When Chloe and Lucifer’s investigation into the murder of a diamond thief points to one of Ella’s brothers as the main suspect, Ella is driven to prove her brother’s innocence and recruits an unlikely ally. Meanwhile, Linda is upset when Charlotte comes to her for help and Detective Pierce hashes out his issues with Amenadiel.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x14

Episodes.Intro: When a best-selling novelist is murdered, Lucifer and Chloe discover that her books are based on real people from her past, and must infiltrate her high school reunion in order to catch her killer. Meanwhile, Amenadiel and Linda struggle with making their relationship public.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x15

Episodes.Intro: When a murder investigation reveals the dark side of Hollywood, Chloe puts her life on the line to protect an innocent victim. Then, Lucifer comes up with a hell-raising scheme to help Cain, but when Amenadiel and Maze get involved, things don’t quite go as planned.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x16

Episodes.Intro: When a superstar singer’s life is threatened, the team is thrust into the world of big-ticket stadium shows, crazed fans and divas, giving Lucifer a run for his money. Meanwhile, Charlotte tries to help Linda and Maze repair their friendship.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x17

Episodes.Intro: After Lucifer removes his wings yet again, Linda becomes concerned that he is too focused on tracking down the Sinnerman and neglecting his own well-being. Tensions continue to rise between Lucifer and Chloe, but they realize they must put their differences aside to solve a case in which Lucifer takes a sudden interest. Once Detective Pierce’s past is revealed though, everyone realizes that the Sinnerman is much more dangerous than they thought.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x2

Episodes.Intro: After talking to Lucifer and Linda, Maze realizes that she is looking for more out of life and decides to head to Canada for a tricky case. Chloe however, becomes concerned when she feels that Maze is being deceived by a scheming conman. Upon further investigation, Lucifer and Chloe make a stunning realization when they find that their target may be much closer than they thought.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x3

Episodes.Intro: When a youth counselor is found murdered, Lucifer and Chloe venture into the world of high-end reform programs to find the killer. Meanwhile, Amenadiel adjusts his lifestyle in an attempt to help Lucifer, and Chloe questions Lt. Pierce’s feelings towards her.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x4

Episodes.Intro: When a food chemist is found dead, Lucifer and Chloe’s investigation pits them against an unexpected face – criminal defense attorney Charlotte Richards. Everyone is caught off guard when they see her back in the precinct. As Lucifer tries to understand her return, he makes a shocking discovery that helps solve the case.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x5

Episodes.Intro: When Lucifer discovers Candy has gone missing, he hightails it to Las Vegas with Ella in tow. They work to find her, but interesting secrets could compromise the investigation. Meanwhile, Chloe is upset that Lucifer left on her birthday.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x6

Episodes.Intro: A reporter seeks revenge when he discovers Lucifer has been sleeping with his estranged wife; a serial killer from Lucifer’s past resurfaces.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x7

Episodes.Intro: When a murder is connected to a celebrity dating app, Lucifer and Chloe question all they know about the world of social media in order to solve the case. Meanwhile, Ella tries to avoid Charlotte, and Amenadiel helps Linda deal with the death of her ex-husband.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x8

Episodes.Intro: Lucifer is worried when he realizes that recipients of his favors start to turn up dead. After he and Chloe investigate, they are finally brought face-to-face with the Sinnerman. Meanwhile, Detective Pierce returns to work after taking a bullet, Charlotte finds a new career and Amenadiel has a new love interest.
Episodes.Name: Lucifer 3x9

Name: Lucifer

Links.Name: Marriage is Not the Happy Ending
Memories are Remembered at Your Convenience

Intro: Choi Ban Do and Ma Jin Joo are both 38-years-old and a married couple. Choi Ban Do has been burdened with being the breadwinner and Ma Jin Joo is a housewife with low self-esteem. Even though they loved each other when they married, they now hate each other. They both regret marrying at such a young age. The couple travel through time and find themselves as 20-year-old university students, when they met for the first time.
Name: Go Back Couple

Intro: Their mission is simple: Find a cure. Stop the virus. Save the world. When a global pandemic wipes out eighty percent of the planet’s population, the crew of a lone naval destroyer must find a way to pull humanity from the brink of extinction.

Episodes.Intro: Sixteen months after thwarting the coup in America, Nathan James must face yet another global disaster. The question remains, where in the world is Tom Chandler?
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x1

Episodes.Intro: Chandler confronts his enemy — and his personal demons — in a final showdown, with the fate of humanity on the line.
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x10

Episodes.Intro: Having lost their only lead, the crew of Nathan James continues their search for an item that could save the world. Chandler immerses himself in a mission for revenge.
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x2

Episodes.Intro: Nathan James’s crew searches for a precious item leading them to a strange place of opulence and violence where they cross paths with a most unexpected ally.
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x3

Episodes.Intro: The crew searches for one of their own as enemies close in on all sides. Slattery is haunted by visions of the past.
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x4

Episodes.Intro: Nathan James is diverted from their mission when they receive a suspicious distress call from a fishing trawler.
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x5

Episodes.Intro: With an enormous storm on the horizon, Nathan James must navigate an equally terrifying threat in order to make it to safety.
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x6

Episodes.Intro: The search continues with a reconnaissance mission but things turn violent when an old foe resurfaces.
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x7

Episodes.Intro: An undercover mission in the land of the dead leads to disturbing revelations about Dr. Vellek’s sinister plans.
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x8

Episodes.Intro: The crew of Nathan James faces a threat that will test the limits of their Naval tactics and strategies.
Episodes.Name: The Last Ship 4x9

Name: The Last Ship

Intro: In the broadcasting world, writers report news of things that have already occurred or are unfolding: they tell it like it is, without any control over transpiring events. 32-year-old news writer Na Mi Rae is the exception to the rule: she meets her future self who wants to change the events of her present life, namely advising her younger self not to marry news anchor Kim Shin. With this in mind, young Mi Rae pursues a vastly different path in life, one full of hopes and dreams. But what’s news to Mi Rae is that when you change even a small part of history, all of history changes along with it.

Episodes.Intro: Na Mi Rae’s fate changes when her future self travels back in time to convince her to change her life.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x1

Episodes.Intro: Mi Rae tries to find a more specific goal for her future. The entire broadcasting team goes on a trip with award money from reporting the subway incident.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x10

Episodes.Intro: Mi Rae runs into trouble during her undercover job at the bar. Joo Hyun tries to make sure Mi Rae stays away from Kim Shin.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x11

Episodes.Intro: When Kim Shin finds out about his future with Mi Rae, he begins to distance himself from her.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x12

Episodes.Intro: Se Joo reveals his true identity to the entire company. Kim Shin considers an offer for an anchor position with NTN Broadcasting in order to stay away from Mi Rae.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x13

Episodes.Intro: Mi Rae attempts to get closer to Se Joo after giving up on Kim Shin. Future Mi Rae prepares to return to her time.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x14

Episodes.Intro: When Future Mi Rae learns that her attempt to change her future is futile, she regrets separating Kim Shin and Mi Rae; however it may be too late to get them back together.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x15

Episodes.Intro: Kim Shin must choose whether or not to report on an issue that may bring about his downfall Future Mi Rae “predicted”.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x16

Episodes.Intro: Despite her warnings, Mi Rae finds herself at YBS Broadcasting Station.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x2

Episodes.Intro: Mi Rae meets her new rival, Seo Yoo Kyung, a reporter who’s after both Kim Shin and Park Se Joo.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x3

Episodes.Intro: Kim Shin and Mi Rae both find themselves becoming attracted to one another after having ominous dreams about being a couple.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x4

Episodes.Intro: Future Mi Rae’s attempt to get Kim Shin relocated to New York backfires when Miranda has plans of her own.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x5

Episodes.Intro: A large scale attack on the Seoul subway system gives Mi Rae and Kim Shin the chance to save a hundred people – and hit the highest viewership ratings for their show so they wouldn’t be relocated.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x6

Episodes.Intro: After the subway incident, Kim Shin and the broadcasting crew decide to try creating a completely new show concept. Se Joo prepares a special event for Mi Rae with Yoo Kyung’s help.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x7

Episodes.Intro: Things are awkward between Mi Rae and Kim Shin until they’re forced to work together overnight in a haunted house.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x8

Episodes.Intro: Joo Hyun tries to convince Mi Rae to go to another broadcasting station in order to keep her away from Kim Shin.
Episodes.Name: Marry Him If You Dare 1x9

Name: Marry Him If You Dare

Intro: A supernatural romance about a woman who can see the future in her dreams, and a prosecutor who fights to stop these future events from happening. The heroine has dreams about unfortunate events that will happen to other people, and the hero is a prosecutor who runs around trying to prevent her tragic visions from coming true.

Episodes.Intro: Hong Joo’s dreams always come true. She dreams of hugging a man whom she has never met and is shocked at her actions. On the night of Valentine’s Day, she is worried about her mom and hurries home to see her. Jae Chan has a dream about Hong Joo. He feels that he must prevent the events of his dreams from actually happening and tries his best to make sure that the accident never happens.
Episodes.Name: While You Were Sleeping 1x1

Name: While You Were Sleeping

Intro: Inevitably, everybody gets hurt at some point in their lives. There are different remedies for different types of wounds, and as time elapses, these remedies start to become less effective. This is a story about a man who created a shield for his broken heart. Since the day his heart broke, he has been living inside a shell. One day, he encounters a being unlike any other, and by interacting with her, he slowly learns how to break out of his shell.
Name: I Am Not a Robot

Intro: A wealthy man and a poor stunt girl fall in love. But things get complicated when their souls become inexplicably swapped and dark secrets surface.

Episodes.Intro: Successful businessman Joo Won has to take the actress Chae Rin to Oska, the famous singer, also his cousin, to prevent a scandal. But instead of Chae Rin, he actually takes her stunt double Gil Ra Im to the hotel.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x1

Episodes.Intro: Unable to forget Ra Im, Joo Won decides to see her for three months, which garners his mother and Oska’s disapproval.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x10

Episodes.Intro: Joo Won and Ra Im break up, but they both harbor feelings for each other. Passive aggressiveness and confrontation ensue between Oska and Seul.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x11

Episodes.Intro: Joo Won’s mother threatens to send Ra Im to another country if Joo Won does not start going on blind dates again.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x12

Episodes.Intro: At the mountain retreat that the action school goes to, Ra Im realizes how attracted she is to Joo Won. Oska finds out who leaked his plagiarized song.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x13

Episodes.Intro: Romance develops between Ra Im and Joo Won. When it rains again, Ra Im and Joo Won switch bodies, causing a series of mix ups.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x14

Episodes.Intro: With no choice, Ra Im and Joo Won reveal their secret to Oska and Jong Soo. Ra Im gets Joo Won to audition for Dark Blood in her place.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x15

Episodes.Intro: Ra Im rushes to Joo Won’s side after his claustrophobia attack, missing her audition for Dark Blood.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x16

Episodes.Intro: Ra Im tries to break up with Joo Won after learning the truth from his mother. She wins the starring role in Dark Blood.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x17

Episodes.Intro: Only magic can save Ra Im and Joo Won, but when Joo Won wakes up, he reverts back to his 21-year old self and does not recognize Ra Im.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x18

Episodes.Intro: Things start to look up for Oska both personally and professionally with Seul. Joo Won regains his memory and runs back to Ra Im.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x19

Episodes.Intro: Being relieved the scandal with his ex Chae Rin is solved, another ex of Oska turns out to be a candidate as his new director. And Joo Won can’t stop thinking about the stuntwoman, does he like Gil Ra Im?
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x2

Episodes.Intro: Ra Im and Joo Won get married despite his mother’s disapproval. Seul professes her love for Oska during his big concert.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x20

Episodes.Intro: Joo Won starts to follow Ra Im and he invites her for a lunch. After being rejected, he’s determined to stick with her and even comes to the action school where she’s working. But then he finds out how different their worlds are.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x3

Episodes.Intro: Joo Won insults Ra Im for her lack of wealth, but he can’t get her out of his mind. Oska tries to recruit singer-composer Tae Sun to be his protegee.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x4

Episodes.Intro: Oska isn’t pleased to find that his ex Seul is the director of his music video. A bike race gone wrong leads to surprising consequences for Joo Won and Ra Im.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x5

Episodes.Intro: Joo Won and Ra Im try to figure out how to switch back without arousing suspicion from others.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x6

Episodes.Intro: Still stuck in each other’s bodies, Joo Won and Ra Im have to live out each other’s lives, but their differing personalities confuse the people around them.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x7

Episodes.Intro: Ra Im and Joo Won use their new-found positions to annoy each other and play with Oska and Seul’s feelings.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x8

Episodes.Intro: A rainstorm allows Ra Im and Joo Won to switch back to their lives, but remnants of the other’s presence still remain. Oska is rocked by a plagiarism scandal.
Episodes.Name: Secret Garden 1x9

Name: Secret Garden

Links.Name: Dipper and Mabel vs. the Future

Intro: Twin brother and sister Dipper and Mabel Pines are in for an unexpected adventure when they spend the summer helping their great uncle Stan run a tourist trap in the mysterious town of Gravity Falls, Oregon.

Episodes.Intro: Twins Dipper and Mabel Pines visit their eccentric great-uncle for a summer in Gravity Falls, Oregon, where he operates the world’s most bizarre museum. As soon as the twins arrive in Gravity Falls, they discover something amiss in the remote town.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x1

Episodes.Intro: After being challenged to a video game battle by Robbie, Dipper is shocked when his favorite playable fighter, Rumble McSkirmish, comes to life to defend him. But Dipper soon loses control over Rumble McSkirmish and has to find a way to stop him.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x10

Episodes.Intro: Dipper is self-conscious that Mabel is taller than him and seeks a magic solution. Meanwhile Lil’ Gideon takes advantage of Dipper’s and Mabel’s height discrepancy.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x11

Episodes.Intro: Dipper and Mabel go trick-or-treating in the summer and encounter a candy-loving monster who threatens to devour them if they don’t bring him sweet things to eat.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x12

Episodes.Intro: Stan leaves Mabel in charge of the Mystery Shack while he is gone and the power goes to her head.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x13

Episodes.Intro: While Stan, Dipper, Mabel and Soos are falling in a bottomless pit, they tell stories to pass the time.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x14

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S01E15 The Deep End.mp4

Episodes.Intro: When Mabel befriends a cute merman trapped in the public pool, she’s determined to help him out. Meanwhile, Dipper decides to volunteer as a lifeguard to see Wendy.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x15

Episodes.Intro: The twins discover a hidden room inside the Mystery Shack and compete over who should have it.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x16

Episodes.Intro: When Mabel discovers that her favorite boy band is actually a bunch of imprisoned clones, she sets them free, only to decide on keeping them for herself. Meanwhile, Dipper is convinced that Robbie plans to brainwash Wendy with a secret message hidden inside one of his songs.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x17

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S01E18 Land Before Swine.mp4

Episodes.Intro: When Waddles is snatched by a prehistoric beast, Dipper, Mabel, Stan, Soos, and Old Man McGucket must journey to a mysterious land trapped in time to rescue him.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x18

Episodes.Intro: Dipper, Mabel, and Soos must travel through Grunkle Stan’s mind to defeat a tricky dream demon summoned by Lil Gideon.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x19

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S01E02 The Legend of the Gobblewonker.mp4

Episodes.Intro: When Dipper and Mabel hear rumors of a sea monster that lives at the bottom of the local lake, they enlist Soos to take them on a boating expedition to prove it really does exist.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x2

Episodes.Intro: Li’l Gideon swindles the Mystery Shack away, forcing Grunkle Stan and the kids to move in with Soos. While Stan weighs how he can still care for his grandniece and nephew, they decide to take on Gideon.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x20

Episodes.Intro: When someone tampers with Mabel’s life-size wax statue of Grunkle Stan, she and Dipper set out to find the culprit. Meanwhile, Grunkle Stan mourns over the loss of his wax doppelganger.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x3

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S01E04 The Hand That Rocks the Mabel.mp4

Episodes.Intro: Dipper and Mabel discover that their seemingly cherubic new neighbor, Lil’ Gideon, happens to be the town’s adored psychic. But when Lil’ Gideon guilts her into dating him, she and Dipper soon learn that his cuteness can fade all too quickly.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x4

Episodes.Intro: Dipper is invited by Wendy and her teen friends on a trek that leads to an abandoned convenience store that may be haunted.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x5

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S01E06 Dipper vs Manliness.mp4

Episodes.Intro: In a quest to attain manliness, Dipper ventures into the forest to battle the notorious Multi-Bear. Meanwhile, Mabel tries to teach Grunkle Stan how to be attractive to women, particularly the waitress in the local diner, Lazy Susan.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x6

Episodes.Intro: Stan throws a big weekend party to promote the Mystery Shack. Dipper makes clones of himself to impress Wendy. Mabel fights for the Party Queen title in honor of her two friends.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x7

Episodes.Intro: When Dipper and Mabel discover evidence that the reported town founder is a hoax, they set out to expose the historical cover-up and prove that Mabel’s silliness is not a bad thing.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x8

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S01E09 The Time Travelers Pig.mp4

Episodes.Intro: Dipper wants to correct a mistake he made in the past with assistance from a time machine. Mabel is overjoyed when she wins a pet pig at a fair.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 1x9

Episodes.Intro: The Pines family is starting to get everything back to normal after the Lil’ Gideon incident. They throw a “Mystery Shack Is Back” party, but some unwelcome guests intend to crash it.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x1

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E10 Northwest Mansion Mystery.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Pacifica enlists Dipper’s help to rid the Northwest Mansion of a ghost before he wreaks havoc on her fancy party.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x10

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E11 Not What He Seems.mkv

Episodes.Intro: After agents Powers and Trigger take Stan into custody, Dipper and Mabel begin to wonder how much they actually know about their Grunkle Stan.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x11

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E12 A Tale of Two Stans.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Cornered underneath the Mystery Shack, Stan must finally reveal the secrets of his past and his mysterious portal to Dipper and Mabel.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x12

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E13 Dungeons Dungeons and More Dungeons.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Dipper finds an unlikely friend to join him with his newest obsession, a board game called “Dungeons, Dungeons & More Dungeons.”
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x13

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E14 The Stanchurian Candidate.mkv

Episodes.Intro: When Grunkle Stan decides to run for mayor, Dipper and Mabel have their work cut out for them trying to turn their gaffe-prone uncle into the perfect candidate.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x14

Episodes.Intro: A new threat leads Mabel to venture into the enchanted realm of the unicorns. Meanwhile, Dipper learns an unexpected twist about the enigmatic Bill Cipher.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x15

Episodes.Intro: Grunkle Stan takes the kids with him on a road-trip to sabotage all the other tourist traps in Oregon.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x16

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E17 Dipper and Mabel Vs The Future.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Mabel makes plans for her and Dipper’s 13th birthday party; Dipper ventures below the town and discovers its most shocking secret.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x17

Episodes.Intro: Bill has returned to take down the Pines family. But this time he has brought some of his friends with him.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x18

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E19 Weirdmageddon Pt 2 Escape From Reality.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Dipper, Soos and Wendy must save Mabel from a strange new world, while Bill’s forces plan their next move.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x19

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E02 Into The Bunker.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Dipper’s secret journal pages lead him and the gang to the author’s hidden bunker where they find themselves face-to-face with a mysterious figure from Gravity Falls’ lore.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x2

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E20 Weirdmageddon 3 Take Back The Falls.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Ford discovers Bill’s true motives and a final confrontation with Bill leads to the Pines family’s ultimate fate and greatest sacrifice.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x20

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E03 The Golf War.mkv

Episodes.Intro: After being belittled by Pacifica one too many times, Mabel challenges her to a miniature golf-off which gets a tad out of control when some local residents offer their help.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x3

Episodes.Intro: Mabel decides to put on a sock puppet rock opera to impress a local puppeteer, but her show goes awry when Dipper’s drive to uncover more of the journal’s secrets leads to a supernatural disaster.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x4

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E05 Soos and The Real Girl.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Soos needs a date for his cousin Reggie’s engagement party and looks to a dating simulator game to help him talk to girls.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x5

Episodes.Intro: In three separate mysterious tales, Stan is cursed by a Witch, Waddles accidentally eats a bowl of brain-enhancing jelly and builds a machine that allows him to speak, and Mabel faces her fear of claymation.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x6

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E07 Society of The Blind Eye.mkv

Episodes.Intro: The kids, along with Old Man McGucket’s help, discover there is a secret society in Gravity Falls.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x7

Episodes.Intro: Blendin returns to face off with Dipper and Mabel in a futuristic battle that could trap them forever in time jail.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x8

Links.Name: Gravity Falls S02E09 The Love God.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Mabel takes matchmaking too far when she steals a love potion from a real Love God.
Episodes.Name: Gravity Falls 2x9

Intro: I Can Hear Your Voice is a 2013 South Korean television series starring Lee Bo-young, Lee Jong-suk, and Yoon Sang-hyun. It aired on SBS from June 5 to August 1, 2013, on Wednesdays and Thursdays at 21:55 for 18 episodes.

Episodes.Intro: Park Soo Ha met Jang Hye Sung when he was a child of eight when she stood witness to his father murder. He has been looking for her ever since then.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x1

Episodes.Intro: Hye Sung finally reunites with Soo Ha after a year of no contact, only to find him suspect to a murder and a with serious case of amnesia.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x10

Episodes.Intro: Hye Sung and Gwan Woo work together again to help with Park Soo Ha’s case.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x11

Episodes.Intro: Do Hyun and Gwan Woo both find evidence that Min Joon Gook may still alive.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x12

Episodes.Intro: Soo Ha hides the fact that he remembers everything. Min Joon-gook appears to call Hye-sung’s home phone to check if she still lives there.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x13

Episodes.Intro: Hye Sung debates on whether to tell Do Hyun about her birth parents.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x14

Episodes.Intro: Do Yeon got confused about her real identity and in turns trying to find out the truth by herself.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x15

Episodes.Intro: Case of Hwang Dal Joong takes turn in this episode where the decision whether he is guilty or not regarding the case of stabbing a ghost (his wife that was presumed dead).
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x16

Episodes.Intro: Min Joon Gook lures Hye Sung into his trap by lying that he kidnapped Soo Ha.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x17

Episodes.Intro: Min Joon Gook promises to tell his whole story if Gwan Woo agrees to become his defense attorney again.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x18

Episodes.Intro: Jang Hye Sung gets hired as a public defender. Her first case involves Park Soo Ha’s classmate, Go Sung Bin.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x2

Episodes.Intro: To find evidences of Sung Bin’s innocence, Hye Sung and Gwan Woo visit Sung Bin’s school dressed as high school students.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x3

Episodes.Intro: Min Joon Gook is planning his revenge on Hye Sung. Meanwhile, Hye Sung and Gwan Woo both receive a case involving twin brothers.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x4

Episodes.Intro: Hye Sung and Gwan Woo work together on the case involving the twins. Meanwhile, Min Joon Gook moves away.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x5

Episodes.Intro: Soo Ha tells Hye Sung that the twins planned the murder, therefore Hye Sung agrees to help Do Hyun prove the twins are guilty.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x6

Episodes.Intro: Cha Gwan Woo tells Hye Sung that he likes her and that they should date.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x7

Episodes.Intro: Hye Sung’s mother is murdered and Gwan Woo is assigned to Min Joon Gook’s case.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x8

Episodes.Intro: Unable to accept the verdict for Min Joon Gook’s case, Soo Ha takes the matter into his own hands, but the consequences are far more severe than he or Hye Sung could have imagined.
Episodes.Name: I Hear Your Voice 1x9

Intro: Writers that lived under Japanese rule in the 1930’s are reincarnated into a bestselling writer who is in a slump, a mysterious ghostwriter and an anti-fan of the bestselling writer.

Intro: Seven noble families fight for control of the mythical land of Westeros. Friction between the houses leads to full-scale war. All while a very ancient evil awakens in the farthest north. Amidst the war, a neglected military order of misfits, the Night’s Watch, is all that stands between the realms of men and icy horrors beyond.

Episodes.Intro: Jon Arryn, the Hand of the King, is dead. King Robert Baratheon plans to ask his oldest friend, Eddard Stark, to take Jon’s place. Across the sea, Viserys Targaryen plans to wed his sister to a nomadic warlord in exchange for an army.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x1

Episodes.Intro: With Ned dead, Robb vows to get revenge on the Lannisters. Jon must officially decide if his place is with Robb or the Night’s Watch. Daenerys says her final goodbye to Drogo.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x10

Episodes.Intro: While Bran recovers from his fall, Ned takes only his daughters to Kings Landing. Jon Snow goes with his uncle Benjen to The Wall. Tyrion joins them.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x2

Episodes.Intro: Lord Stark and his daughters arrive at King’s Landing to discover the intrigues of the king’s realm.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x3

Episodes.Intro: Eddard investigates Jon Arryn’s murder. Jon befriends Samwell Tarly, a coward who has come to join the Night’s Watch.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x4

Episodes.Intro: Catelyn has captured Tyrion and plans to bring him to her sister, Lysa Arryn, at The Vale, to be tried for his, supposed, crimes against Bran. Robert plans to have Daenerys killed, but Eddard refuses to be a part of it and quits.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x5

Episodes.Intro: While recovering from his battle with Jamie, Eddard is forced to run the kingdom while Robert goes hunting. Tyrion demands a trial by combat for his freedom. Viserys is losing his patience with Drogo.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x6

Episodes.Intro: Robert has been injured while hunting and is dying. Jon and the others finally take their vows to the Night’s Watch. A man, sent by Robert, is captured for trying to poison Daenerys. Furious, Drogo vows to attack the Seven Kingdoms.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x7

Episodes.Intro: Eddard and his men are betrayed and captured by the Lannisters. When word reaches Robb, he plans to go to war to rescue them. The White Walkers attack The Wall. Tyrion returns to his father with some new friends.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x8

Episodes.Intro: Robb goes to war against the Lannisters. Jon finds himself struggling on deciding if his place is with Robb or the Night’s Watch. Drogo has fallen ill from a fresh battle wound. Daenerys is desperate to save him.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 1x9

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E01 The North Remembers.mkv

Episodes.Intro: As Robb Stark and his northern army continue the war against the Lannisters, Tyrion arrives in King’s Landing to counsel Joffrey and temper the young king’s excesses. On the island of Dragonstone, Stannis Baratheon plots an invasion to claim his late brother’s throne, allying himself with the fiery Melisandre, a strange priestess of a stranger god. Across the sea, Daenerys, her three young dragons, and the khalasar trek through the Red Waste in search of allies, or water. In the North, Bran presides over a threadbare Winterfell, while beyond the Wall, Jon Snow and the Night’s Watch must shelter with a devious wildling.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x1

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E10 Valar Morghulis.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Tyrion awakens to a changed situation. King Joffrey doles out rewards to his subjects. As Theon stirs his men to action, Luwin offers some final advice. Brienne silences Jaime. Arya receives a gift from Jaqen. Dany goes to a strange place. Jon proves himself to Qhorin.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x10

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E02 The Night Lands.mkv

Episodes.Intro: In the wake of a bloody purge in the capital, Tyrion chastens Cersei for alienating the king’s subjects. On the road north, Arya shares a secret with Gendry, a Night’s Watch recruit. With supplies dwindling, one of Dany’s scouts returns with news of their position. After nine years as a Stark ward, Theon Greyjoy reunites with his father Balon, who wants to restore the ancient Kingdom of the Iron Islands. Davos enlists Salladhor Saan, a pirate, to join forces with Stannis and Melisandre for a naval invasion of King’s Landing.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x2

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E03 What Is Dead May Never Die.mkv

Episodes.Intro: At the Red Keep, Tyrion plots three alliances through the promise of marriage. Catelyn arrives in the Stormlands to forge an alliance of her own, but King Renly, his new wife Margaery, and her brother Loras Tyrell have other plans. At Winterfell, Luwin tries to decipher Bran’s dreams.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x3

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E04 Garden of Bones.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Joffrey punishes Sansa for Robb’s victories, and Tyrion scrambles to temper the king’s cruelty. Catelyn entreats Stannis and Renly to unite against the Lannisters. Dany and her khalasar arrive at the prosperous city of Qarth. Tyrion coerces a relative into being his eyes and ears. Arya and Gendry are taken to Harrenhal, where their lives are in the hands of Ser Gregor Clegane. Stannis orders Davos to smuggle Melisandre into a secret cove.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x4

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E05 The Ghost of Harrenhal.mkv

Episodes.Intro: The Baratheon rivalry ends, driving Catelyn to flee and Littlefinger to act. At King’s Landing, Tyrion’s source alerts him to Joffrey’s defense plan – and a mysterious secret weapon. Theon sails to the Stony Shore to prove he’s worthy to be called Ironborn. At Harrenhal, Arya receives a promise from Jaqen H’ghar, one of the prisoners she saved from the Gold Cloaks. The Night’s Watch arrive at the Fist of the First Men, an ancient ringfort where they hope to stem the wildings’ advance.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x5

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E06 The Old Gods and the New.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Theon completes his master stroke. In King’s Landing, the Lannisters send Myrcella off to be married. Arya comes face to face with a surprise visitor. Dany vows to take what is hers. Robb and Catelyn receive crucial news. Qhorin gives Jon a chance to prove himself.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x6

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E07 A Man Without Honor.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Jamie meets a distant relative. Daenerys receives an invitation to the House of the Undying. Theon leads a search party. Jon loses his way in the wilderness. Cersei counsels Sansa.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x7

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E08 The Prince of Winterfell.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Theon receives a visitor. Arya asks her third and last death from Jaqen. While Stannis’ army is reaching its destination, Davos is offered a reward. Betrayal befalls Robb.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x8

Links.Name: Game of Thrones S02E09 Black Water.mkv

Episodes.Intro: Tyrion and the Lannisters fight for their lives as Stannis’ fleet assaults King’s Landing.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 2x9

Episodes.Intro: Jon meets the King-Beyond-the-Wall while his Night Watch Brothers flee south. In King’s Landing, Tyrion wants a reward, Margaery shows her charitable nature, Cersei arranges a dinner party, and Littlefinger offers to help Sansa. Across the Narrow Sea, Daenerys starts her journey west.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 3x1

Episodes.Intro: Joffrey challenges Tywin. Bran tells a ghost story. In Dragonstone, mercy comes from strange quarters. Daenerys waits to see if she is a conqueror or a liberator.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 3x10

Episodes.Intro: Sansa says too much. Shae asks Tyrion for a favor. Jaime finds a way to pass the time, while Arya encounters the Brotherhood Without Banners.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 3x2

Episodes.Intro: Tyrion shoulders new responsibilities. Jon is taken to the Fist of the First Men. Daenerys meets with the slavers. Jaime strikes a deal with his captors.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 3x3

Episodes.Intro: Trouble brews among the Night’s Watch at Craster’s. Margaery takes Joffrey out of his comfort zone. Arya meets the leader of the Brotherhood. Varys plots revenge on an old foe. Theon mournfully recalls his missteps. Daenerys deftly orchestrates her exit from Astapor.

Episodes.Intro: The Hound is judged by the gods. Jaime is judged by men. Jon proves himself. Robb is betrayed. Tyrion learns the cost of weddings.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 3x5

Episodes.Intro: Tywin plans strategic unions for the Lannisters. Melisandre pays a visit to the Riverlands. Robb weighs a compromise to repair his alliance with House Frey. Roose Bolton decides what to do with Jaime Lannister. Jon, Ygritte, and the Wildlings face a daunting climb.

Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 3x8

Episodes.Intro: Robb presents himself to Walder Frey, and Edmure meets his bride. Jon faces his harshest test yet. Bran discovers a new gift. Daario and Jorah debate how to take Yunkai. House Frey joins with House Tully.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 3x9

Episodes.Intro: Tyrion welcomes a guest to King’s Landing. At Castle Black, Jon Snow finds himself unwelcome. Dany is pointed to Meereen, the mother of all slave cities. Arya runs into an old friend.

Episodes.Intro: Circumstances change after an unexpected arrival from north of the Wall. Dany must face harsh realities. Bran learns more about his destiny. Tyrion sees the truth about his situation.

Episodes.Intro: Tyrion lends Jaime a hand. Joffrey and Margaery host a breakfast. At Dragonstone, Stannis loses patience with Davos. Ramsay finds a purpose for his pet. North of the Wall, Bran sees where they must go.

Episodes.Intro: Tyrion ponders his options. Tywin extends an olive branch. Sam realizes Castle Black isn’t safe, and Jon proposes a bold plan. The Hound teaches Arya the way things are. Dany chooses her champion.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 4x3

Episodes.Intro: Dany balances justice and mercy. Jaime tasks Brienne with his honor. Jon secures volunteers while Bran, Jojen, Meera and Hodor stumble on shelter.

Episodes.Intro: Cersei and Tywin plan the Crown’s next move; Dany discusses future plans; Jon Snow begins a new mission.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 4x5

Episodes.Intro: Stannis and Davos set sail; Dany meets with supplicants; Tyrion faces down his father.

Episodes.Intro: Tyrion gains an unlikely ally; Daario asks Dany to allow him to do what he does best; Jon’s warnings about the vulnerability of the Wall are ignored; Brienne follows a new lead.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 4x7

Episodes.Intro: Unexpected visitors arrive in Mole’s Town. Littlefinger’s motives are questioned. Ramsay tries to prove himself to his father. Tyrion’s fate is decided.

Episodes.Intro: Jon Snow and the Night’s Watch face a big challenge.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 4x9

Episodes.Intro: Cersei and Jaime adjust to a world without Tywin. Varys reveals a conspiracy to Tyrion. Dany faces a new threat to her rule. Jon is caught between two kings.

Episodes.Intro: Stannis marches. Dany is surrounded by strangers. Cersei seeks forgiveness. Jon is challenged.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 5x10

Episodes.Intro: Arya arrives in Braavos. Podrick and Brienne run into trouble on the road. Cersei fears for her daughter’s safety in Dorne as Ellaria Sand seeks revenge for Oberyn’s death. Stannis tempts Jon. An adviser tempts Daenerys.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 5x2

Episodes.Intro: In Braavos, Arya sees the Many-Faced God. In King’s Landing, Queen Margaery enjoys her new husband. Tyrion and Varys walk the Long Bridge of Volantis.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 5x3

Episodes.Intro: The Faith Militant grow increasingly aggressive. Jaime and Bronn head south. Ellaria and the Sand Snakes vow vengeance.
Episodes.Name: Game of Thrones 5x4

Episodes.Intro: Dany makes a difficult decision in Meereen. Jon recruits the help of an unexpected ally. Brienne searches for Sansa. Theon remains under Ramsay’s control.

Episodes.Intro: Arya trains. Jorah and Tyrion run into slavers. Trystane and Myrcella make plans. Jaime and Bronn reach their destination. The Sand Snakes attack.
